    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巴佛兰奇遇记：夺回你的至强胡须！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394880/extras/4893378bab9f0ea1c78a364912837512.avif?t=1738157526\" width=616 height=204 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在荒诞离奇的巴佛兰世界里，男人的胡须象征着至高无上的力量。而你的胡须，却在你人生最重要的一天前夜被人夺走了！在五大独特场景中，与成群结队的敌人和强悍头目激战，誓要夺回属于你的标志性胡须！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394880/extras/a7e678f7ff5086097e6c737068705905.webp?t=1738157526\" width=616 height=3 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394880/extras/cbd06825ae980847bc88b9b2657f6a86.avif?t=1738157526\" width=616 height=64 /></span><br>🎯 <strong>经典街机体验</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏忠实还原了经典光枪射击游戏的爽快手感，支持手柄、触屏操作以及光枪设备，让你随心所欲选择最适合自己的方式畅玩！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394880/extras/1cea383520872ccccb2883d25220ffaf.poster.avif?t=1738157526\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394880/extras/1cea383520872ccccb2883d25220ffaf.webm?t=1738157526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394880/extras/1cea383520872ccccb2883d25220ffaf.mp4?t=1738157526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394880/extras/a7e678f7ff5086097e6c737068705905.webp?t=1738157526\" width=616 height=3 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394880/extras/717fcc4e020637efe196d385706d37f2.avif?